menu_38025_1=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >The antidote is hidden in the shoes? It…</font><font face="Default" color="#8fd6ef" >(It's better to discuss it with Elder Brother Qingyuan in order to avoid being cheated…)</font>
menu_38027_1=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >You should have said it earlier.</font>
menu_38027_2=<font face="Default" color="#8fd6ef" >（Remember to take the white pill before you go to the Pavilion just in case…）</font>
menu_38028_1=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >I know why you are really here. I hope you will surrender peacefully.</font>
menu_38029_1=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Jing De… </font><font face="Default" color="#ffffff">Elder Brother is…</font>
menu_38030_1=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff">Thank you</font><font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >.</font>
